author: A Vox in the Void
description:
As the Decepticons launch a devastating assault on New Cybertronia, Ultra Magnus struggles to hold the Autobots’ last stronghold together in the absence of Optimus Prime. When a hidden Omega-level threat emerges—an engineered asteroid on a collision course with Earth—Magnus calls upon the Wreckers for a desperate counter-mission.

WRECKING CREW - WRITTEN BY MATTHEW TUCKER

NARRATED AND PRODUCED BY A VOX IN THE VOID

MUSIC BY EPIDEMIC SOUND AND THE WONDERFULLY TALENTED @titantracks2662 

A huge thankyou to Flint for helping me with the video editing! you are a legend. Also a shoutout to my friend Gis for coming up with the series name! 

This is the first of hopefully many re-imaginings of popular 1980's cartoons and the beginning of the 'CINEVOX' series.
